title: End of Summer
lastfmSummary: End of Summer is a single by Australian music project Tame Impala, released on July 25, 2025, marking Kevin Parker’s return after a five-year hiatus from solo releases. Following a series of high-profile collaborations with artists such as Thundercat and Justice, “End of Summer” arrives as a potential lead single for Tame Impala’s highly anticipated fifth studio album.
